              <p>The recognition of professional qualifications and regulation of professions: policy statement <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/recognition-of-professional-qualifications-and-regulation-of-professions-policy-statement"><u>https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/recognition-of-professional-qualifications-and-regulation-of-professions-policy-statement</u></a></p>
            </content>
